                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <para>Universal joints have the following features:</para>
            <randlist type="bullet">
                <item>
                    <para>A lubed-for-life design.</para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>Equipped with nylon thrust washers, located at the base of each bearing cup, which control end
                        play, positions the needle bearings and improves grease movement.
                    </para>
                </item>
            </randlist>
